{"tid":1361602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛最新攻勢：出老解，元朗班人會點點點，散佈恐嚇資訊","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T18:23:06.000Z","uid":60665,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f949ec31eace519c8fb0565f14a702149d92cc1f","tid":1361602,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩有個恐嚇post俾連仔del左，連仔好波<br />\n焦土派唔work，分化post玩唔掂，而家班五毛已經轉玩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">散佈恐嚇資訊</span><br />\n一大班人話好快出老解，又話元朗會點點點<br />\n好明顯而家五毛改左策略想用恐懼黎打擊依場運動，因為分化焦土依d舊招已經俾大家悉穿左<br />\n今日夜晚突然大量話解放軍就黎會出，最多咪同中共一齊死之類講到似層層<br />\n我初頭都信信地<br />\n再見到頭先個自稱now既恐嚇post，起一起條友底同見到張殘到好似係唔知邊到執返黎既now員工證，我就知道五毛又轉左新玩法<br />\n唔好俾恐嚇post嚇到唔出黎，只係五毛又轉左新招玩恐嚇嚇人唔好出黎"},{"pid":"341292553fac0b7b855c19abdc292fd0016f5d25","tid":1361602,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b83f2b13dc03c31ddf7243e3c491d7a386cd1216","tid":1361602,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648d291a23dce60a6fcd0663377646a8a85a182a","tid":1361602,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"咁樣就驚唔敢行岀黎，同生活係集中營有乜分別<br />\n不自由 毋寧死！"},{"pid":"2bc5b329d5f3cecfb853252faff3fba83cd9fd36","tid":1361602,"uid":245441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"三毛就快得番一毛了 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6mtMde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6mtMde.png&h=0f5b92b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"375e820486d8f34653f845b9a568d4242d7079ae","tid":1361602,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"又散播恐怖"},{"pid":"1b0043594f70dc2ee0fdafdf250d947a00fc32df","tid":1361602,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85069b919d0d8e2eee21dbd259975882c4f005db","tid":1361602,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9627aa28649ebf58e8f4257b7fc4c22d0478bfd","tid":1361602,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fab1750d0bac7dac46d95bbc2bc5327f71e39ba9","tid":1361602,"uid":270954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ddf8f9812830f47a1edbe80cc4a8134352192f","tid":1361602,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要製造仇恨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0G9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=545b34db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"dbaf5d59c1c9115ecb308934e429ea3f722eb473","tid":1361602,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"一係又話收到牛屎佬風要做野<br />\n<br />\n星期一又二百刀手<br />\n<br />\n又話要血洗連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n有D無里頭爭執又話白打黑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4432cf6b06547d515da9f1de915cbfed1f03876a","tid":1361602,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:58:56.000Z","msg":"好多五毛根本唔想727係勇武 唔想有人去圍村 又想香港人繼續示弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c6e74d4880141864f579c9ca1ef4c11710601c","tid":1361602,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede46f36c872730f9e9ca7bc29ee57ac35c24f36","tid":1361602,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"其實唔明點解個個都唔驚解放軍，同埋出老解外國會出手，我認同明知輸都要一戰的諗法，但我覺得老解一出一定一國一制，而且有好多後生仔會走唔切而死。"},{"pid":"f596bf0f6748279853e6f0d3458ea3826b02ce2d","tid":1361602,"uid":60665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ede46f36c872730f9e9ca7bc29ee57ac35c24f36","tid