:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:11:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10a3f472c3979d4c7e80d91077a855c68af086a6","tid":1361602,"uid":20372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"總之照出喇 和理非回合 遇到攻擊先還手<br />\n村唔好入  如果硬要入就大聲問一問先 俾入先入 入去唔係打燒拆 入去擺低文宣 講句我地知道係河妖策劃 一齊聲討佢 就走得  唔俾入就算"},{"pid":"c6b1be303fb140bc256491b8df74407b92e844fb","tid":1361602,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"雖然呢d消息可能係散播恐怖，但有危險最緊要自己判斷安全與否"},{"pid":"9fca0d104b8524dc573be539509989540602d773","tid":1361602,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"中共d垃圾招數對付d封閉既愚民就得<br />\n而家資訊流通呢d爛招真係唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336a2e7d45b603e987cd5bd71b7d44810235abce","tid":1361602,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6gdXsA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6gdXsA.png&h=c2c247e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}